{"type": "article", "id": 14501, "title": "香料植物清洁刷", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-06T07:12:58Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 14, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000326nAypYQmlwq7jBVCt.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t米兰的设计师 alessandra baldereschi 用香料植物做了一套家用清洁刷，植物夹在两块橡胶做的薄片中间，除了充当清洁的刷子，还可以发挥这些植物的特性，比如装上薄荷或者甘菊都有防蚊虫的功效，而迷迭香可以抗菌，薰衣草除了除臭外也能防腐。他还另外用硬纸板做了 17 种不同形状和颜色的“袋子”，用图形来标注植物的功用，可谓脑洞奇大。<a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/design/alessandra-baldereschi-grandmother-tips-aromatic-tools-09-04-2015/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142020vXRICnM8OSTr0Dqs.jpg\" width=\"950\" height=\"849\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.89368421\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142020QTVPZOFBHgokEwyG.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"595\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.72738386\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261420211VmIRfrtuMgNy6As.jpg\" width=\"950\" height=\"672\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70736842\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142021dKRUAuoISWMwH6xQ.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"474\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5794621\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142021nzAp8rgoK3hZxjNU.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"543\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66381418\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}